description:
Seven classic DCU titles — THE ATOM AND HAWKMAN, THE QUESTION, PHANTOM STRANGER, STARMAN, THE POWER OF SHAZAM!, CATWOMAN and WEIRD WESTERN TALES — are resurrected alongside GREEN ARROW #30 and ADVENTURE COMICS #7 in this BLACKEST NIGHT tie-in hardcover!

They are driven by darkness of death itself. They seek to blot out the light of life forever. And they use the resurrected bodies and minds of the dead to do it.

They are the Black Lantern Corps. And the shadow of the Blackest Night has fallen on every corner of the DC Universe!

In these chilling stories, the Black lanterns have come for the hearts of an army of the DCU's most powerful heroes and villains.

The Souls of Superboy and Green arrow... Catwoman's deadliest enemy an the Atom's closest allies... the legacies of Starman and the Question... the weirdest, wildest Western heroes... the magic of the Phantom Stranger... the power of Shazam!

All will be used to to fuel the fire of the Black Lanterns. And the lives of all they touch will be changed forever...
name: HC

volume.name: Blackest Night: Rise of The Black Lanterns
